fields.name: Black Trousers 1
fields.description: These beauties would look incredible accompanying almost any combination of clothing. The sleek and slender lines narrow from the hips and taper to the ankle, giving a real Hollywood feel to the wearer.

fields.name: Black Trousers 2
fields.description: This pair of dazzling leg wear are simply a voucher for success in the business World. The classic lines mixed with the leather look enable any accomplished power dresser to move up the leagues and bowl into the boardroom with real panache.

fields.name: Black Trousers 3
fields.description: With the feminine vibe of these trousers it would take a man of colossal inter-personal stature to wear them, but they really are a must buy for any man. The flared bottoms would enchant any passer by with there debonair ambiance and graceful vibe.

fields.name: Black T-Shirt 1
fields.description: This T-Shirt may initially seem expensive but, what is hard to tell from the image is, it's knitted from wool. This type of fine weave is too good for rugs,  or toupee's, its only good enough for someone hungry enough to look like the most stylish fashionisto on the street.

fields.name: Black T-Shirt 2
fields.description: This T-shirt is a fine item for a young girl. It is hard wearing, fashionable and probably suited for a Goth. Any parent would feel safe knowing their daughter isn't going out with daubing's on their garments.

fields.name: Blue T-Shirt 1
fields.description: This low priced garment offers the look of feel of life with high rollers at a price that'll make you think the seller is bonkers. But the only person that's bonkers is YOU, if you don't get yourself a slice of this fashion pie.

fields.name: Blue T-Shirt 2
fields.description: This classic T-shirt would be a fine gift for any young man. Its hard wearing, durable nature ensures it is robust enough to handle any outside play, whilst it's elegant look will ensure wouldn't look out of place mixing in any social circles.

fields.name: Blue T-Shirt 3
fields.description: This is the T-shirt that has featured in so many blockbuster movies we simply can't list them, we'll need you to do the homework on this one. But rest assured, it was loads, really. So spend your pennies on this gleaming, 24 carat, fashion diamond. Then prepare to be mobbed when you go out in public wearing the most famous T-shirt in the movie mogul’s World!

fields.name: Green Skirt 1
fields.description: This is the type of skirt that could help Bucks Fizz reform but it can do so much more. With the bow tie waist and pleats this skirt could be worn to a job interview or perhaps in the hands of a more cavalier lady, to an all night rave in a muddy field. Either way, you'll be the green skirted wonder woman and who wouldn’t want that.

fields.name: Green Skirt 2
fields.description: This dainty number will have you looking like the bell of the ball, whether you go dancing or to a football match. It's design is famous World wide and by wearing it, it'll serve as a beacon to others that you've entered the highest echelons of the fashion World.

fields.name: Green Trousers 1
fields.description: If you want to be at the forefront of male fashion, then strap yourself into a pair of these immense pantaloons. Green is a powerful colour, so only purchase these if your sure you can tame the passion flame that ignites in others when they see you in them.

fields.name: Green Trousers 2
fields.description: If your child has white trousers and keeps getting grass stains on them these are a must, you'd be a fool not to. Seriously a massive fool, so get your wallet out or pave your garden, and you won't pave your garden for £4.99 sunshine.

fields.name: Green T-Shirt 1
fields.description:
This is almost a T-shirt give-away! This incredible price is only for these particular T-shirts and it's virtually a steal. 

We should mention that in no way are these items anything to do with the great Green T-Shirt robbery that happened to our competitors recently. Seriously, not in ANY way. REALLY! Look, just get you bargain T-shirt and don't mention it to anyone....

fields.name: Red Skirt 1
fields.description: Who doesn't want a red skirt? You lot pipe down, this is for the people that do. This skirt is fresh like a summers day, it will radiate a sunny disposition to all those that  have the pleasure of seeing you in it.

fields.name: Red Skirt 2
fields.description: A red skirt that will be an exciting addition to any child's wardrobe. It's amazing to think that it is made from recycled tin cans. They said it wasn't possible, but they were proved wrong, it goes to show, never say no can do.

fields.name: Red Trousers 1
fields.description: These versatile bloomers are a must for any domestic goddess. Not only do they afford the owner the luxury of being seen as the epitome of high class fashion, they also have the capacity to act as back up curtains should the need arise. Please be aware that a curtain rail is not included in purchase.

fields.name: Red Trousers 2
fields.description: These red trousers are an amazing fashion statement for your child, he'll leave his peers in his dust as he drives himself through his days gleefully wearing these. So if you want to create fashion envy in other parent, dress your mite in these and watch those parents faces match the trouser as they smoulder away as they watch your red panted wonder be the star of the show.

fields.name: Red Trousers3
fields.description:
Do you know what people say about a man in red trousers? Well ignore them and have a look at these almighty beasts of the fashion World.

The red colour and leather look would have a thunderous mental impact on those that encountered you. These are the ultimate power pants, worn only by a special section of society. Only buy if you can handle the power, be warned, Darth Vader was Anakin Skywalker before he got his pair.

fields.name: Yellow Trousers 1
fields.description: These enrapturing yellow britches are ripe for picking off the fashion carousel. Although they look like distressed banana's its impossible to have made a fashion slip up choosing them. They are ideal for wearing when you need to leave early from a lame party, just raise your palm in the face of the host, start to walk out and over your shoulder simply say “Banana Split”.

fields.name: Red T-Shirt 1
fields.description: This classic T-shirt would be rightly cherished by it owner despite the fact its Man Utd red. It is made from reclaimed seaweed so would be a great gift for any environmentally minded youngster, or pet lobster.

fields.name: Red T-Shirt 2
fields.description: One for all you female Chris de Burgh  fans, "The Lady in Red" and all that, right. If you want to attract your own ageing crooner or even the guy that plays jazz on his mini Casio keyboard on Friday evenings at the local Cab rank, this will be your fashion based love magnet.

fields.name: White Shirt 1
fields.description: If you want to dominate the darwinesque jungle that is your workplace, wrap yourself in this vibrant and stylish shirt and instantly turn from the hunted into the hunter! You'll morph from your timid self into the fighting lion beast that knows no fear - Grrrrrr!

fields.name: White Shirt 2
fields.description: Ever wondered how to truly stand out from the crowd? Well you can stop stroking your chin and staring wistfully out the window as we have the answer! The bold colouring of this shirt will stagger friends and foes alike, so don't follow the crowd like a sheep, stand out in white.

fields.name: White Shirt 3
fields.description: This mystical shirt enables the wearer to secretly transition from giving the impression of being 'casual and in control' to 'hard worker' with a single manual adaption. This incredible transition is made via the rolling up (or down) or the sleeves. So if you want to manage what your boss thinks of with Ninja like stealth, this perception shifting shirt is for you.

fields.name: White Skirt 1
fields.description: Ever wanted people to think you recycle your table cloths? Yes? Well that's great news as we've just got hold of a skirt that can fulfil your fashion needs. This dainty number comes with a complementary dinner set and a pack of paper doilies.

fields.name: White Trousers 1
fields.description: These crisp beauties would hold their own in Vegas, Miami or a Milton Keynes shopping centre. This gives the owner a veritable smorgasbord of places to show them off. We supply these trousers for you to travel in, you choose the destination.

fields.name: White Trousers 2
fields.description:
These airy strides would be an ideal gift for any woman who wanted to go out on the town after gaining a particular Karate grade.

So if you know any ladies going through the Mr. Miyagi experience, once they have sanded the floor, creosoted the fencing, painted the house and waxed the floor - you could make their graduation extra special by gifting them these.

fields.name: White T-Shirt 1
fields.description: A white T-shirt is a royal treat for any young man. So take the money you had saved for their PS4 Christmas gift and spend it all on as many of these as you can. Its worth remembering that on being told what you've done a lot of youngster won't have felt as happy as this before, so they may become confused and resort to crying and saying things like "Whyyyyyyyyyyyyyy!!" and "Noooooooooooooooooooooo", but give them a few days and that PS4 will be forgotten as they gaze into their wardrobe and see all the gleaming white garments on display.

fields.name: Yellow Trousers 2
fields.description: Most parents wouldn't want their son to be taunted into adulthood for a choice of trousers they made. But if your not in that group then we have a real treat for you, because these would be the perfect trousers for you to send your child to school in. Once through the gates, within minutes they'll become "Mr Yellow Pants" to their friends, a nickname your child will cherish for the next 20 years.

fields.name: Yellow T-Shirt
fields.description: If you'd like to be seen at night this is the t-shirt for you!

fields.name: White T-Shirt 2
fields.description: This is a perfect gift for a woman who is in your life - perhaps its your Wedding Anniversary, the birth of your first child or perhaps its her birthday. Whatever the occasion she'll find it difficult (maybe even impossible) to contain her joy at receiving a gift like this on a special occasion, we think that's all the more reason to treat her again with another one of these whenever subsequent special occasions arise.
